{"visualizations":{"viz_1NAjX7Bd":{"type":"splunk.markdown","options":{"markdown":"# Welcome to the SPLing Bee!

Overview:

- You will need a computer connected to the internet
- You will need to login with given user credentials
- Points are awarded quickest correct answers (earliest = most points) as well as number of submissions (correct on first submit = most points)
- You will need to rename answer field to **"answer"** and use the ```|sendanswer``` custom command in order to send answers"}},"viz_9uzOXsuA":{"type":"splunk.image","options":{"preserveAspectRatio":true,"src":"splunk-enterprise-kvstore://62791bb453d09000974765b1"}},"viz_vWsyQtYc":{"type":"splunk.markdown","options":{"markdown":"General Data Files Introduction

1. [server_power.csv](/en-US/app/spling_bee/search?q=%7C%20inputlookup%20server_power.csv)
 (Lookup) - Contains sample values for server power usage.

 ```
 | inputlookup server_power.csv
 ```

1. [milk.csv](/en-US/app/spling_bee/search?q=%7C%20inputlookup%20milk.csv)
 (Lookup) - Contains sample values for historical milk production.
 ```
 | inputlookup milk.csv
 ```

3. [iron.csv](/en-US/app/spling_bee/search?q=%7C%20inputlookup%20iron.csv) (Lookup) - Contains sample values for historical iron production.
 ```
 | inputlookup iron.csv
 ```

4. [batting.csv](/en-US/app/spling_bee/search?q=%7C%20inputlookup%20batting.csv) (Lookup) - Contains MLB statistics.
 ```
 | inputlookup batting.csv
 ```

5. [car_data.csv](/en-US/app/spling_bee/search?q=%7C%20inputlookup%20car_data.csv) (Lookup) - Contains car data such as speed and rpms.
 ```
 | inputlookup car_data.csv
 ```
6. [stocks.csv](/en-US/app/spling_bee/search?q=%7C%20inputlookup%20stocks.csv) (Lookup) - Contains stock data for volume and bids.
 ```
 | inputlookup stocks.csv
 ```
7. [spotify_chart.csv](/en-US/app/spling_bee/search?q=%7C%20inputlookup%20spotify_chart.csv) (Lookup) - Contains music data from Spotify.
